[[File:Hyperspacetunnel.png|thumb|250px|The iconic bright blue swirls of a simu-tunnel]]
A '''simu-tunnel''',<ref name="SoloOG">''[[Solo: A Star Wars Story The Official Guide]]''</ref> also known as a '''hyperspace tunnel''',<ref name="Beware the Nameless">''[[The High Republic: Beware the Nameless]]''</ref> or as a '''hyper tunnel''',<ref name="Creatures">''[[Star Wars: Creatures Big & Small]]''</ref> was a tunnel-like pocket of [[realspace]] allowing safe travel through the alternate dimension known as [[hyperspace]]. Although most beings needed [[hyperdrive]] technology to produce such tunnels, the [[purrgil]] created them naturally. From the traveler's point of view, a simu-tunnel looked like a spiral of [[Color|blues]].<ref name="SWIntel">{{SW|url=news/star-wars-inside-intel-hyperspace|text=''Star Wars'' Inside Intel: Hyperspace - Updated|int=Star Wars Inside Intel}}</ref>

[[Naley Frifa]] had a [[tattoo]] of a stylized hyperspace simu-tunnel on her neck and upper torso.<ref name="SoloOG" />

